### Rules: Try to guess the 5-letter mystery word. Enter your guess into the text box using all capital letters.
The color of the letters in the result indicates the outcome of your guess: - Green - the correct letter in the correct position - Yellow - the word contains this letter, but not in this position - Grey - the word does not contain this letter
_You get 6 guesses!_
Congratulations! You won!
